Class AbstractJCloudScaleServerRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.infosys.jcloudscale.server.AbstractJCloudScaleServerRunner
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JCloudScaleServerRunner

    public abstract class AbstractJCloudScaleServerRunner
extends Object
    Abstract superclass for JCloudScaleServerRunners to eliminate static references to getInstance(), so that different implementations of JCloudScaleServerRunner can be used.
